title: Regulators will launch a 'full-fledged assault' against Facebook and Twitter, tech investor Paul Meeks predicts
text: Paul Meeks, who's known for running the world's largest tech fund during the late 1990s, said he won't invest in social media stocks right now.

title: Top Trending Stocks This Week As Markets Hit Record Highs
text: The indices are on a five-day winning streak, on pace for a sixth up day in a row. With more earnings on tap, Q.ai's deep learning algorithms have rated this week's top trending stocks.

title: Don't Let This Fight With Apple Spook You Away From Facebook Stock
text: Apple is planning on a major change to its online ads. But investors in Facebook stock should not worry much.
